WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
Tap "Browse Brands" and search 150+ Pakistani brands.

00:05.000 --> 00:09.000
Open a brand and find a product you love.

00:09.000 --> 00:16.000
Copy the product link — use the Pakistani site for the real PKR price.

00:16.000 --> 00:26.000
Back in PakPoshak, paste it: category, price & sizes auto-fill — then save.

00:26.000 --> 00:32.000
Your all-in total shows in BDT.

00:32.000 --> 00:39.000
Add your name, WhatsApp, and delivery address.

00:39.000 --> 00:46.000
Review, then Confirm & Submit — you get an Order ID.

00:46.000 --> 00:54.000
Pay with bKash, Nagad, Upay or Rocket.

00:54.000 --> 01:00.500
Upload your payment slip — done!
